OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784306880
OL,3,CStaffordshire residents warned about
OL,4,Ctoxic algae in country park water
OL,6,FPeople are being warned to stay away
OL,7,Ffrom country park water in
OL,8,FStaffordshire after blue-green algae
OL,9,Fwas spotted.
OL,11,FThe County Council says that there
OL,12,Fhave been reports at both Chasewater
OL,13,Fand Cannock Chase Country Park.
OL,15,FWhat is blue-green algae and why
OL,16,Fshould you report it?
OL,18,FIt can pose a serious risk to animals
OL,19,Fsuch as dogs if they drink or swim in
OL,20,Fthe affected water.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
